## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may have inherent biases based on their institutional affiliations or the focus of their research. Additionally, the complexity of violent crime means that not all contributing factors can be fully explored in this brief report. Further research is recommended to explore additional variables and to update findings as new data becomes available.

